name: Kids Summer Camp (3Days a Week)
description:
Send the Kiddos for a Half day summer camp three days a week to enjoy a variety of crafts!

Projects will consist of Slime, Ceramics, Wood, Dreamcatchers, Canvas Paintings, String Art, String Painting, Canvas Totes, Tie-Dye Pillow Case, and Tie-Dye Beach Towel.

Morning Camps run from 9:30am - 12 noon.

Afternoon Camps run from 1:30pm - 4pm.

Ages 5 - 14.

Pricing is $150 for One Child. Second Child is $135 and Every Child after is only $125.

name: Kids One Day Crafting Camp
description:
Send the Kiddos for a One Day Craft Camp to enjoy a variety of FUN crafts!

Projects will consist of Slime, Ceramic, Dreamcatcher, and Tie-Dye Pillow Case or Beach Towel.

Ages 5 - 14.

Pricing is $65 for One Child & $55 for Other Siblings.
